:Namespace Prepl
‚ćĚ Prepl: A programmable REPL server for Dyalog APL
‚ćĚ Inspired by Clojure's prepl
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Protocol (pure APLAN):
‚ćĚ   Input:  APL expression, newline-terminated
‚ćĚ   Output: APLAN namespace, newline-terminated:
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'ret' ‚čĄ val: 1 2 3)         ‚ÄĒ return value
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'ret')                        ‚ÄĒ no displayable result (shy/void)
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'err' ‚čĄ en: 11 ‚čĄ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR' ‚čĄ dm: (...))
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Usage:
‚ćĚ   2 ‚éēFIX 'file:///path/to/Prepl.apln'
‚ćĚ   Prepl.Start 4200          ‚ćĚ blocking
‚ćĚ   Prepl.LoadConga            ‚ćĚ pre-load on main thread (‚éēCY needs thread 0)
‚ćĚ   tid‚ÜźPrepl.Start&4200      ‚ćĚ on new thread (& is an operator: f&arg)
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Loads Conga from workspace if needed.

    ‚éēIO‚Üź1

    LDRC‚Üź‚ć¨           ‚ćĚ Conga instance (set by LoadConga)
    _stop‚Üź0          ‚ćĚ Stop flag
    _buf‚Üź''          ‚ćĚ Receive buffer (v1: single connection)

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Server Lifecycle ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ

    ‚ąá LoadConga
    ‚ćĚ Load and initialize Conga. Copies from ws if not already present.
      :If 9‚Č†‚Ćä#.‚éēNC'Conga'
          'Conga'#.‚éēCY'conga'
      :EndIf
      LDRC‚Üź#.Conga.Init'prepl'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Start port;z
      _stop‚Üź0
      _buf‚Üź''
      :If ‚ć¨‚Č°LDRC ‚čĄ LoadConga ‚čĄ :EndIf   ‚ćĚ Skip if pre-loaded by bootstrap
      :Trap 0 ‚čĄ {}LDRC.Close'prepl' ‚čĄ :EndTrap
      z‚ÜźLDRC.Srv'prepl' '' port 'Raw' 4096
      :If 0‚Č†‚äÉz
          ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl: failed to start on port ',‚ćēport
          :Return
      :EndIf
      ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl listening on port ',‚ćēport
      Loop
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Stop
      _stop‚Üź1
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Loop;wres;rc;obj;evt;data
      :While ~_stop
          wres‚ÜźLDRC.Wait'prepl' 5000
          :If 0‚Č†1‚äÉwres
              :If 100=3‚äÉwres ‚čĄ :Continue ‚čĄ :EndIf   ‚ćĚ Timeout
              ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl: wait error ',‚ćēwres
              :Leave
          :EndIf
          (rc obj evt data)‚Üź4‚ÜĎwres
          :Trap 0
              :Select evt
              :Case 'Connect'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :Case 'Block'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'BlockLast'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'Closed'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :Case 'Error'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :EndSelect
          :Else
              ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl event error:' ‚éēDMX.(EN Message)
          :EndTrap
      :EndWhile
      {}LDRC.Close'prepl'
      ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl stopped'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá obj HandleBlock data;text;idx;expr;response
    ‚ćĚ Buffer incoming data and process complete lines
      text‚Üź'UTF-8'‚éēUCS data
      _buf,‚Üźtext
      :While (‚éēUCS 10)‚ąä_buf
          idx‚Üź_buf‚ć≥‚éēUCS 10
          expr‚Üź(idx-1)‚ÜĎ_buf
          _buf‚Üźidx‚Üď_buf
          :If (0<‚ČĘexpr)‚ąß(‚éēUCS 13)=‚äÉ‚ĆĹexpr    ‚ćĚ Strip CR from CRLF
              expr‚Üź¬Į1‚Üďexpr
          :EndIf
          :If 0<‚ČĘexpr
              response‚ÜźEval expr
              {}LDRC.Send obj('UTF-8'‚éēUCS response,‚éēUCS 10)
          :EndIf
      :EndWhile
    ‚ąá

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Evaluation ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźEval expr;val;ok;‚éēPW;‚éēPP
      ‚éēPW‚Üź32767
      ‚éēPP‚Üź17
      ok‚Üź0
      :Trap 0
          :With #
              val‚Üź‚ćéexpr
          :EndWith
          ok‚Üź1
      :Else
          :If 6=‚éēDMX.EN            ‚ćĚ VALUE ERROR ‚Üí no result (shy/void)
              r‚ÜźRetAPLAN ‚ć¨
          :Else
              r‚ÜźErrAPLAN ‚éēDMX
          :EndIf
      :EndTrap
      :If ok
          :Trap 0
              r‚ÜźRetAPLAN val
          :Else
              :Trap 0
                  r‚ÜźRetAPLAN(‚ćēval)  ‚ćĚ Fallback to display form string
              :Else
                  r‚ÜźRetAPLAN'[serialization failed]'
              :EndTrap
          :EndTrap
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźRetAPLAN val;ns
    ‚ćĚ (tag: 'ret' ‚čĄ val: <value>)  or  (tag: 'ret')  for void
      ns‚Üź‚éēNS''
      ns.tag‚Üź'ret'
      :If ~(0=‚Č°val)‚ąß(0‚ąä‚ćīval)‚ąß(' '‚Č†‚äÉ0‚ćīval)   ‚ćĚ Not ‚ć¨ (void sentinel)
          ns.val‚Üźval
      :EndIf
      r‚ÜźToAPLAN ns
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźErrAPLAN dmx;ns
    ‚ćĚ (tag: 'err' ‚čĄ dm: (...) ‚čĄ en: 11 ‚čĄ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR')
      ns‚Üź‚éēNS''
      ns.tag‚Üź'err'
      ns.message‚Üźdmx.Message
      ns.en‚Üźdmx.EN
      ns.dm‚Üźdmx.DM
      r‚ÜźToAPLAN ns
    ‚ąá

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ APLAN Serialization ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
    ‚ćĚ Converts APL values to Array Notation text that gritt's codec can parse.
    ‚ćĚ Handles scalars, vectors, matrices, namespaces, and nested arrays.
    ‚ćĚ Higher-rank arrays fall back to ‚ćē (display form).

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźToAPLAN val
      :If 9=‚Ćä‚éēNC'val'                      ‚ćĚ Namespace
          r‚ÜźNStoAPLAN val
      :ElseIf 0‚ąä‚ćīval                        ‚ćĚ Empty
          :If ' '=‚äÉ0‚ćīval ‚čĄ r‚Üź'''''' ‚čĄ :Else ‚čĄ r‚Üź'‚ć¨' ‚čĄ :EndIf
      :ElseIf 0=‚ćī‚ćīval                       ‚ćĚ Scalar
          :If ' '=‚äÉ0‚ćīval
              r‚Üź'''',val,''''               ‚ćĚ Character scalar
          :Else
              r‚Üź‚ćēval                         ‚ćĚ Number (‚ćē uses ¬Į and J natively)
          :EndIf
      :ElseIf 1=‚ćī‚ćīval                       ‚ćĚ Vector
          r‚ÜźVecToAPLAN val
      :ElseIf 2=‚ćī‚ćīval                       ‚ćĚ Matrix
          r‚ÜźMatToAPLAN val
      :Else
          r‚Üź‚ćēval                             ‚ćĚ Higher rank: display form fallback
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźVecToAPLAN val;parts
      :If 1‚Č•‚Č°val                             ‚ćĚ Simple (not nested)
          :If ' '=‚äÉ0‚ćīval                    ‚ćĚ Character vector
              r‚ÜźQuoteStr val
          :ElseIf 1=‚ČĘval                     ‚ćĚ Single-element numeric
              r‚Üź'(‚čĄ ',(‚ćē‚äÉval),')'
          :Else                               ‚ćĚ Numeric strand
              r‚Üź‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ',‚ćĶ}/‚ćē¬®val
          :EndIf
      :Else                                   ‚ćĚ Nested vector
          parts‚ÜźToAPLAN¬®val
          :If 1=‚ČĘparts
              r‚Üź'(‚čĄ ',(‚äÉparts),')'
          :Else
              r‚Üź'(',(‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ‚čĄ ',‚ćĶ}/parts),')'
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźMatToAPLAN val;rows;parts
      rows‚Üź‚Üďval
      :If ' '=‚äÉ0‚ćīval                        ‚ćĚ Character matrix
          parts‚ÜźQuoteStr¬®rows
      :ElseIf 1‚Č•‚Č°val                         ‚ćĚ Simple numeric matrix
          parts‚Üź{‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ',‚ćĶ}/‚ćē¬®‚ćĶ}¬®rows
      :Else                                   ‚ćĚ Nested matrix (best effort)
          parts‚Üź{‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ',‚ćĶ}/ToAPLAN¬®‚ćĶ}¬®rows
      :EndIf
      r‚Üź'[',(‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ‚čĄ ',‚ćĶ}/parts),']'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźNStoAPLAN ns;keys;parts
      keys‚Üźns.‚éēNL ¬Į2 ¬Į9
      :If 0=‚ČĘkeys
          r‚Üź'()'
      :Else
          parts‚Üź{‚ćĶ,': ',(ToAPLAN ns‚ćé‚ćĶ)}¬®keys
          r‚Üź'(',(‚äÉ{‚ćļ,' ‚čĄ ',‚ćĶ}/parts),')'
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźQuoteStr str
    ‚ćĚ Quote a character vector for APLAN, doubling internal single quotes
      r‚Üź'''',({‚ćĶ/‚ć®1+‚ćĶ=''''}str),''''
    ‚ąá

:EndNamespace
